* Carnage looked up at Tritan and growled, she didn't like his ton of voice!
Also besides the fact that he had probably already given away her position by now, she was just about ready to throw up her talons in frustration and walk away!
Carnage glared even harder at Tritan, what mission?
Was he sent by some Pred or some Maximal to defend Teltoli, or was he sent by some other force for some reason that she still couldn't understand?
She sighed and snarled at the same time...*

" What mission? Who sent you?"

* Even though she said this in a whisper she knew that his blue form had given her away to Teltoli if nobot else.
She sighed in frustration, just not her day...was  it?!!*
